next to it

1. *Krevetu* je njegova najomiljenija stvar. (The bed is his favorite thing.)
2. Ona je jedva čekala da se spusti na *krevetu*. (She couldn't wait to lie down on the bed.)
3. On je polako puzao prema *krevetu*. (He slowly crawled towards the bed.)
4. Ona je legla u svoj *krevet*. (She lay down on her bed.)
5. On je peškirom pokrio *krevet*. (He covered the bed with a towel.)
6. Kasno uveče, ona se ponovo uvukla u *krevet*. (Late at night, she crawled back into the bed.)